  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：DeepSeek-V3.2-Exp</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4222222222222222\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1152\" data-height=\"486\" data-imgfileid=\"100016016\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=15c5c14e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwkCOEicEwWvCmn9YYdkusLjQtwjhg7Zg6agqWHMrQVAWpvb9HuXx2aWEQaLKfvMMHDDib4vqSoNqSw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★DeepSeek-V3.2-Exp 是 DeepSeek-AI 推出的实验性模型版本，旨在通过引入 DeepSeek 稀疏注意力机制来优化长文本场景下的训练和推理效率。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该版本在保持模型输出质量的同时，显著提升了长文本处理的计算效率。DeepSeek-V3.2-Exp 的训练配置与前一版本 V3.1-Terminus 保持一致，并在多个公共基准测试中表现出与 V3.1-Terminus 相当的性能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/deepseek-v3-2-exp-2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/deepseek-v3-2-exp-2</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：MinerU2.5</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5555555555555556\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" data-height=\"646\" data-imgfileid=\"100016018\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1b517e18&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwkCOEicEwWvCmn9YYdkusLjh93u5Ovz6Iicfc1SBzokTN1NTpibibeeCvhyyX2nkZgTtibECo0t9nmqicQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★MinerU2.5是一个拥有1.2B参数的视觉语言模型，专注于文档解析，具有高效的计算能力和先进的准确性。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型采用两阶段解析策略：首先对降采样图像进行全局布局分析，然后对原始分辨率的图像进行细粒度内容识别，包括文本、公式和表格。通过大规模多样化的数据引擎进行预训练和微调，MinerU2.5在多个基准测试中表现优于通用和领域特定模型，同时保持较低的计算开销。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/mineru2-5\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/mineru2-5</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：Wan-Alpha</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5527777777777778\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1158\" data-height=\"640\" data-imgfileid=\"100016019\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f64e732b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwkCOEicEwWvCmn9YYdkusLjkia8QdkKRzmdGs5nv91S0Z5icyQEPiciad42zaVsyYVBbPqfdsqta5PA9A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Wan-Alpha 是一个高质量的文本生成视频项目，支持 Alpha 通道，能够生成各种场景的视频，具有准确且清晰的透明度渲染能力。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">特别是，它可以合成多样的半透明对象、发光效果以及细致的细节如头发等。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/wan-alpha\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/wan-alpha</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">④项目：Ring-1T-preview</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.537962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1152\" data-height=\"620\" data-imgfileid=\"100016015\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2bb10e30&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwkCOEicEwWvCmn9YYdkusLjlbuSCicYaibGxdPE5HRhpygpgXdMuw4luzDG7vm8lmmAz30ibP8eLYYWg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Ring-1T-preview 是一个由 inclusionAI 开发的预览版语言模型，基于 1 万亿参数的基础模型，专注于自然语言推理能力的提升。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型在大规模增强学习的训练过程中展现了强大的推理能力，尤其是在数学竞赛和代码生成任务中表现出色。Ring-1T-preview 采用了高效的 MoE 架构，并在 20T 语料库上完成了预训练。尽管该模型已经展示了强大的推理能力，但仍存在语言混合、重复推理和身份误解等问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/ring-1t-preview\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/ring-1t-preview</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️框架平台、必备工具</span></strong></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：unity-mcp</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.55\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1152\" data-height=\"634\" data-imgfileid=\"100016017\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3c7a89f2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwkCOEicEwWvCmn9YYdkusLjj7HibcSAaVcuic91I4Xm9vKUv6c5EyWbibpVfttMMQw6RbUpoL6VvAw6w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Unity MCP是一个Unity的MCP服务器，允许MCP客户端（如Claude Desktop或Cursor）执行Unity编辑器操作。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目通过本地MCP客户端使AI助手能够直接与Unity编辑器交互，提供管理资产、控制场景、编辑脚本和自动化任务的工具。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/unity-mcp\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/unity-mcp</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">⚙️ Robotics 开发</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：FSDrive</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3453703703703704\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1152\" data-height=\"398\" data-imgfileid=\"100016020\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fbf83595&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwkCOEicEwWvCmn9YYdkusLjF0XqaR07WezcLodEl6c7UfD74nGzbfWyWRJlz7PfzltvYw3fCGyKUQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★FutureSightDrive（FSDrive）项目提出了一种时空协同推理（CoT）方法，使得自动驾驶车辆能够在端到端的框架下进行视觉化的轨迹规划。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目通过最小化数据需求，将视觉生成与理解统一起来，首次推动了自动驾驶向视觉推理的方向发展。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/fsdrive\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/fsdrive</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章总结了近期开源的 DeepSeek 稀疏注意力模型、文档解析 VLM、文本生成视频、万亿参数 LLM 等多个 AI 项目。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章总结了近期开源的 DeepSeek 稀疏注意力模型、文档解析 VLM、文本生成视频、万亿参数 LLM 等多个 AI 项目。",
  "summary": "本文汇总了近期多个重要的开源技术项目。其中包括 DeepSeek-AI 推出的实验性语言模型 DeepSeek-V3.2-Exp，其通过稀疏注意力机制提升了长文本处理效率。还介绍了专注于文档解析的视觉语言模型 MinerU2.5，以及支持 Alpha 通道的高质量文本生成视频项目 Wan-Alpha。此外，文章还提到了 inclusionAI 开发的万亿参数语言模型 Ring-1T-preview，该模型在大规模增强学习的训练过程中，在数学竞赛和代码生成任务中表现出色。在工具方面，收录了 Unity MCP 服务器，使 AI 助手能直接与 Unity 编辑器交互。最后，还介绍了自动驾驶领域中采用时空协同推理方法的 FSDrive 项目，旨在实现视觉化轨迹规划。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "DeepSeek-V3.2-Exp 模型通过稀疏注意力机制提升长文本处理效率",
      "explanation": "该实验性模型在保持性能的同时，显著优化了长文本场景下的训练和推理计算效率，对处理大规模文本数据有重要意义。"
    },
    {
      "point": "MinerU2.5 视觉语言模型实现高效精准的文档解析",
      "explanation": "该模型采用两阶段解析策略，能对文档进行全局布局分析和细粒度内容识别，在文档自动化处理方面具有高效率和高准确性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Wan-Alpha 项目实现高质量文本生成视频，支持 Alpha 通道渲染",
      "explanation": "该项目能生成具有准确透明度渲染的视频，特别适用于合成半透明对象和细致细节，拓展了视频生成技术的应用范围。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Ring-1T-preview 大型语言模型展现强大推理能力",
      "explanation": "基于万亿参数和 MoE 架构，该模型在大规模增强学习后，在数学竞赛和代码生成等复杂推理任务中表现突出。"
    },
